title: Kristen Kish
itunes:title: Kristen Kish
description:
Chef, author, and TV-personality Kristen Kish talks with Anna about the pasta that brought them together, the formative experience of winning Top Chef, leadership in the kitchen, growing up in Michigan, recognizing love, quarantine weddings, her TV show Fast Foodies and more. Later in the episode, Anna and Kristen talk with Madison who is trying to figure out why nearly every conversation with her mother seems to end badly and if she might somehow be responsible. Next, they talk with Natalie who doesn’t know if she should move on from an unbalanced relationship or continue to hope that it becomes something more.


If you have a question and would like to talk with Anna, please reach out! Go to: unqualified.com/talk-with-anna
